data.enText: a vegetable with green leaves around a large hard white head of flowers

tr: compact head of white undeveloped flowers
a plant having a large edible head of crowded white flower buds

value.def: Cauliflower is a large round vegetable that has a hard white centre surrounded by green leaves.

trans: (因多次遭殴打而永远肿胀的)菜花耳
